original_title: Billy Blanks Tae Bo: Amped Fat Burn Accelerator
overview: Billy Blanks s Tae Bo system has been helping people lose weight and look great for years and Billy has continuously incorporated new techniques into his his work-outs to keep them fresh and effective. From this development comes his signature "Cardio Bursts" routines that add an extra push to his already effective Tae Bo moves. This program will help participants kick and punch their way to leaner better bodies.
title: Billy Blanks Tae Bo: Amped Fat Burn Accelerator
